br.ufrn.exminer.util

Class ExceptionStacktraceExtractor

  • java.lang.Object
    • br.ufrn.exminer.util.ExceptionStacktraceExtractor

  • public class ExceptionStacktraceExtractor
extends java.lang.Object
    This class extracts a stack trace from the text. To do so it parses the text using regular expressions and heuristics. It connects all causes that are related to a top level exception.

      • extractStacktraces

        public static java.util.ArrayList<java.lang.String> extractStacktraces(java.lang.String text,
                                                       boolean cleanChars,
                                                       boolean joinCause)
        This method extract the stack trace (top level exception and its causes) from a piece of text.
        Parameters:
        text - the string containing or not the Java exception stack trace to be mined
        cleanChars - when true indicates that some characters ($#@) will be replace during mining. This replacement improves the precision of the parses based on regular expression.
        joinCause - when true connects all causes of the exception being thrown.
        Returns:
        return all frames that compose the stack trace.
